                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-2083</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The module &lt;tt&gt;surefire-shared-utils&lt;/tt&gt; uses &lt;tt&gt;maven-shade-plugin&lt;/tt&gt; to relocate a number of Apache dependencies under new package names.&lt;/p&gt;

